			<h2><strong>A BUSINESS BUILT AND RUN ON DATA</strong></h2>
			<h1>McPen story</h1>
			<p>
			McPen wanted a customized operations management system. Combining their existing POSs, Frames and other retail data, they were able to identify retail solutions specific to their business. </p>
